                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7018Kawinamakonnen">Kawina makʷannǝn baʿāla gerā wa-kawina kāhǝn ʿabiy
          mǝnt wǝʾǝtu (Qǝne of wāzemā-type)</title></desc>
                                    ዋዜ<supplied reason="lost" resp="DN">ማ</supplied>፡ ዘ<supplied reason="lost" resp="DN"/>                            
                                    <l n="1">ከዊነ፡ መኰንን፡ በዓለ፡ ጌራ፡ ወከዊነ፡ ካህን፡ ዐቢይ፡ ምንት፡ ውእቱ፡</l> 
                                    <l n="2">በዕለት፡ አሐቲ፡ አኮኑ፡ ሞቱ፡</l>
                                    <l n="3">እብል፡ አንሰ፡ በሐልዮ፡ እለ፡ ክልኤቱ፡</l>
                                    <l n="4">ኵሉ፡ ክንቱ፡ ኵሉ፡ ክንቱ፡ ኵሉ፡ ክንቱ፡</l>
                                    <l n="5">ንብረቱ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ ዓለም፡ ውእቱ።</l>  
                                </item>
                                <note>Written in an 18th- or 19th-century hand. The name of the author has not been indicated.</note>
                            </list>
